<p><strong>Funding/Support:</strong> This work was supported by an unrestricted educational grant from Sanofi Spain, Leo Pharma, and Rovi; the Scott Schoen and Nancy Adams IGNITE Award from the Mary Horrigan Connors Center for Women’s Health and Gender Biology at Brigham and Women’s Hospital (Dr Bikdeli); and a Career Development Award (938814) from the American Heart Association (Dr Bikdeli).</p>
<p><strong>Role of the Funder/Sponsor:</strong> The funders had no role in the design of the current study, statistical analysis, drafting the manuscript, or the decision to submit.</p>
