<span class="label">33.</span><cite>Anderson DR, Morgano GP, Bennett C, et al. American Society of Hematology 2019 guidelines for management of venous thromboembolism: prevention of venous thromboembolism in surgical hospitalized patients. Blood Adv. 2019;3(23):3898-3944. doi: 10.1182/bloodadvances.2019000975</cite> [<a href="https://doi.org/10.1182/bloodadvances.2019000975" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">DOI</a>] [<a href="/articles/PMC6963238/" class="usa-link">PMC free article</a>] [<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/31794602/" class="usa-link">PubMed</a>] [<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?journal=Blood%20Adv&amp;title=American%20Society%20of%20Hematology%202019%20guidelines%20for%20management%20of%20venous%20thromboembolism:%20prevention%20of%20venous%20thromboembolism%20in%20surgical%20hospitalized%20patients&amp;volume=3&amp;issue=23&amp;publication_year=2019&amp;pages=3898-3944&amp;pmid=31794602&amp;doi=10.1182/bloodadvances.2019000975&amp;" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Scholar</a>]</li>
